OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight with gusty winds to start with
OL,7,Fbut easing through the night. Cloudier
OL,8,Fin the far west with a few spots of
OL,9,Frain. Staying mild with most places
OL,10,Fstaying in double figures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudier start with showery
OL,13,Frain pushing eastwards followed by the
OL,14,Frisk of thunderstorms. Some brighter
OL,15,Fspells developing in the west through
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Lighter winds than of
OL,17,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
