OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,6,Fmore changeable into the weekend with
OL,7,Fshowers, or longer spells of rain,
OL,8,Fpossibly thundery at times.
OL,9,FTemperatures generally returning
OL,10,Fcloser to average.
